annotations.title: Rabo de Galo Brazil’s #2 Most Popular Cocktail

textContent:
2oz (60ml) Cachaca
.75oz (22.5ml) Cynar
.75oz (22.5ml) Sweet Vermouth
Lime Twist

Stir in rocks glass over large ice cube
